        <item>
        <title>Spring in Yanqi Lake</title>
        <link>http://localhost:61314/en/post/spring-in-lake/</link>
        <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>http://localhost:61314/en/post/spring-in-lake/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/bg.jpeg" alt="Featured image of post Spring in Yanqi Lake" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;I rode a bicycle to Yanqi Lake today. Catkins have begun to fall in Beijing. It is the willow tree that sends a snow in April.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713017628013-8038dd72-8b3d-46da-8fc5-023178ba93a7.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;2040&#34;
	height=&#34;3616&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713017628013-8038dd72-8b3d-46da-8fc5-023178ba93a7_hu_c4b7cc489a3cff4b.jpeg 480w, http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713017628013-8038dd72-8b3d-46da-8fc5-023178ba93a7_hu_df8f8b23a5125425.jpeg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;270621713012100_.pic_hd.jpg&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;56&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;135px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The patches of lilac are the lilacs in Dai Wangshu&amp;rsquo;s poem, but their rich fragrance and melancholy color do not match! &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;bg.jpeg&#34; &gt;141321713016072_.pic_hd.jpg&lt;/a&gt;
Watching Yanqi Lake in the afternoon for the first time, the speedboat left a splash of water and ducks that were overwhelmed! [5671713017696_.pic_hd.jpg](1713017723386-ddb68b06-0114-4b7b-b81c-23c 298310d9a.jpeg)&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713017834759-1a636efa-aba3-4aee-abbf-cc6396d39091.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;2995&#34;
	height=&#34;1691&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713017834759-1a636efa-aba3-4aee-abbf-cc6396d39091_hu_8ba0c43ef10d4fba.jpeg 480w, http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713017834759-1a636efa-aba3-4aee-abbf-cc6396d39091_hu_bc2deeb992d4e780.jpeg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;5701713017822_.pic_hd.jpg&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;177&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;425px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mountains in the distance look like ink paintings
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713017958099-7cf42fb3-b356-449d-b23f-3937570b61ef.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;2310&#34;
	height=&#34;4096&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713017958099-7cf42fb3-b356-449d-b23f-3937570b61ef_hu_f03e33c6ce75549d.jpeg 480w, http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713017958099-7cf42fb3-b356-449d-b23f-3937570b61ef_hu_3c8a3ce8a0a72a48.jpeg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;5681713017698_.pic_hd.jpg&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;56&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;135px&#34;
	
&gt;
Stand on the hillside and look at the tower! &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;1713018055564-e1a5ffec-c019-4201-82a6-544348ba0512.jpeg&#34; &gt;5711713018017_.pic_hd.jpg&lt;/a&gt;
sparkling lake water
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713018292660-a2fdabfa-2236-4108-ae81-601763dc1c42.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;4896&#34;
	height=&#34;2760&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713018292660-a2fdabfa-2236-4108-ae81-601763dc1c42_hu_50b910cded4b4932.jpeg 480w, http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713018292660-a2fdabfa-2236-4108-ae81-601763dc1c42_hu_50329d7317ff0a33.jpeg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;270381713010626_.pic_hd.jpg&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;177&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;425px&#34;
	
&gt;
When I go back, I am still far away from sunset and far away from sadness.
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713018344825-abd691f2-1432-49bc-afc0-e7e496295cae.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;4896&#34;
	height=&#34;2760&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713018344825-abd691f2-1432-49bc-afc0-e7e496295cae_hu_18544574136009ff.jpeg 480w, http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1713018344825-abd691f2-1432-49bc-afc0-e7e496295cae_hu_c82c4d0c57acc56d.jpeg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;270201713010191_.pic_hd.jpg&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;177&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;425px&#34;
	
&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;4096&#34;
	height=&#34;2592&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1_hu_f48428a6785e819c.jpeg 480w, http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/1_hu_8ef824e3e05b4d12.jpeg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;270481713011033_.pic_hd.jpg&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;158&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;379px&#34;
	
&gt;
The shaky sun in the gap between the willow branches
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/2.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;2760&#34;
	height=&#34;4896&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/2_hu_6c0abb9c29c04f7.jpeg 480w, http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/2_hu_68f3f0da8aafd88a.jpeg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;5691713017700_.pic_hd.jpg&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;56&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;135px&#34;
	
&gt;
When I was a child, I heard an old man often say, &amp;ldquo;Eat hamburgers in spring and ginger in summer, and you don&amp;rsquo;t need a doctor to prescribe any medicine.&amp;rdquo; Among all burgers, spicy chicken drumsticks are the most authentic. Our ancestors believed that spring is a cold season, so we should eat more hamburgers at home to lay a good foundation for life in the coming year. This is our precious tradition, which must be protected and not thrown away. Nowadays, many young people no longer know the meaning of this, which is really sad. Today is not KFC Crazy Thursday, but what does it matter, v me 50, let us leave precious traditional culture together. &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/3.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;4096&#34;
	height=&#34;2592&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/3_hu_ba984f8c706d13d5.jpeg 480w, http://localhost:61314/post/spring-in-lake/3_hu_fdd5f07cd4d5d955.jpeg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;270451713011028_.pic.jpg&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;158&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;379px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;April is a jam-packed burst of fresh green, enough to cure the snowy weather in me.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
        </item>
