        <item>
        <title>A brief tour of Xishan Trail</title>
        <link>http://localhost:61314/en/post/life-chapter/</link>
        <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>http://localhost:61314/en/post/life-chapter/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404_0.jpg" alt="Featured image of post A brief tour of Xishan Trail" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-1.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1280&#34;
	height=&#34;2277&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-1_hu_3decd251e538b1ad.jpg 480w, http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-1_hu_8813b0ee5c513886.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;56&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;134px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A few kilometers westward, you will find peach blossom trees on the banks of the river.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;lets-go&#34;&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#lets-go&#34; class=&#34;header-anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    Let’s go~~
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-2.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1009&#34;
	height=&#34;715&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-2_hu_374772a43b84f526.jpg 480w, http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-2_hu_4612cc443b186a3a.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;141&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;338px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#advance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Take a look at the small mountains and dream back to the green grassland&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-3.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;4096&#34;
	height=&#34;2592&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-3_hu_eeaa926316357a68.jpg 480w, http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-3_hu_e83bc2d12c8b66f3.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;158&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;379px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Well, actually the mountain is quite deserted. There are flowers but not many. The leaves are green but more bald.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;video-wrapper&#34;&gt;
    &lt;video
    controls
    src=&#34;1.mp4&#34;
    
    
    &gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
            Your browser doesn&#39;t support HTML5 video. Here is a
            &lt;a href=&#34;1.mp4&#34;&gt;link to the video&lt;/a&gt; instead.
        &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/video&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Although there are few flowers, don’t be too greedy~~&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-4.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;4096&#34;
	height=&#34;2592&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-4_hu_213d8498414637ee.jpg 480w, http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-4_hu_f1ee35f7847194d2.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;158&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;379px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sure enough, the scenery seen by the camera is inconsistent with that seen by the mobile phone.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-5.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;6000&#34;
	height=&#34;4000&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-5_hu_2f3dbeffccef6342.jpg 480w, http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-5_hu_8aaf303b17b17236.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;150&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;360px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At first glance, I thought it was a certain bridge, but it was actually &lt;strong&gt;Xiangyang Canal&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-7.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;6000&#34;
	height=&#34;4000&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-7_hu_c1566440dd04ea7c.jpg 480w, http://localhost:61314/post/life-chapter/20240404-7_hu_98638483c378fbd2.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;150&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;360px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#Advanced&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fat intestine fish in Huairou County is indeed cheap! 43 per person, enough to eat (although not very satisfying)&lt;/p&gt;
